  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a small horror game about brutalist architecture in Eastern Europe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326720/extras/541ac30395ccb9a687205ee32d214dac.poster.avif?t=1764154624\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326720/extras/541ac30395ccb9a687205ee32d214dac.webm?t=1764154624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326720/extras/541ac30395ccb9a687205ee32d214dac.mp4?t=1764154624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Brutalism22, you are playing as a regular supermarket worker at the workplace, and suddenly, bombs start to drop. So you are trying to escape the city under attack with your dog, your neighbor, and her daughter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique brutalist architecture</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro-style Eastern European cities and towns.   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scary monsters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several grim, intense locations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30-40 min gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute dog</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326720/extras/91ca6f14d1b48034b8b8e4f00dbf0de1.avif?t=1764154624\" width=620 height=256 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a small horror game about brutalist architecture in Eastern Europe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326720/extras/541ac30395ccb9a687205ee32d214dac.poster.avif?t=1764154624\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326720/extras/541ac30395ccb9a687205ee32d214dac.webm?t=1764154624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326720/extras/541ac30395ccb9a687205ee32d214dac.mp4?t=1764154624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Brutalism22, you are playing as a regular supermarket worker at the workplace, and suddenly, bombs start to drop. So you are trying to escape the city under attack with your dog, your neighbor, and her daughter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique brutalist architecture</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro-style Eastern European cities and towns.   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scary monsters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several grim, intense locations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30-40 min gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute dog</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326720/extras/91ca6f14d1b48034b8b8e4f00dbf0de1.avif?t=1764154624\" width=620 height=256 /></span></p>",
